啦睇醫生，因為成份唔同係醫唔同野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T15:17:19.000Z","msg":"唔該你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實我都知睇醫生先係最正確嘅方法<br />\n但係我嘅情況時好時壞 所以想慳啲錢<br />\n今日放工嘅時候 直頭好似冇咗個魂魄咁<br />\n喺放工附近行嚟行去 明明知道應該行去邊<br />\n但係就係冇動力行過去<br />\n上到車仲控制唔到自己 喊得好犀利<br />\n但係喊完好似舒服晒<br />\n而家冇晒事 非常正常"},{"pid":"ad1e2d9e25f076ba031c5eb84789ef7bc45187ac","tid":2167852,"uid":355756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"914d15ca8db4e1bcbf996154e214091b483c44ac","tid":2167852,"uid":183058,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T12:45:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/health/ak8ong.amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fhealth%2Fak8ong.amp&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu6tywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=d3a79469\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/health/ak8ong.amp</a><br />\n<br />\n暫時食住呢啲先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T15:18:37.000Z","msg":"唔該晒你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都會買啲supplement食住先 <br />\n如果冇好轉就會去睇醫生"},{"pid":"5a1003a7d295a232963d9fb5aa8499d7b6c9bedc","tid":2167852,"uid":355756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78bb729c6ca4e8a4378c69f80c7081dff5744a74","tid":2167852,"uid":61281,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T11:22:02.000Z","msg":"啲藥要醫生出紙先可以合法配，<br />\n搵個好醫生有埋口頭治療吧。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T15:21:50.000Z","msg":"唔該你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係我個情況嘅誘因係生活環境轉變左 <br />\n因為香港日日淪陷、屋企變化好大、同埋武漢肺炎搞到咩都唔做得，所以自己情緒好差，好多時都好痛苦。呢啲大環境都唔係醫生可以改變到。"},{"pid":"029edc0c4e95440cc0c2e5526b9885ac36958939","tid":2167852,"uid":355756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"601fd599980afbda0c8cec30dd59bfc405045771","tid":2167852,"uid":156326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T11:20:31.000Z","msg":"睇醫生<br />\n成藥個劑量多左少左都會出左"},"c